language.dat: customized file for testing “our” languages.
setuptests: some setups for running the tests (source it in your shell)
t2aenc.def: modified from TeX Live, for our tests.
newmongolian.ldf: for the “new” Mongolian patterns.
stupid-wolf-{utf8,cp1251}.tex: test for Mongolian patterns (UTF-8 and legacy).
make-formats.sh: Making formats for pdfTeX and XeTeX.
udhr-{utf8,iso-8859-7}.tex: test for Monotonic Greek (UTF-8 and legacy).
